Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Ethics Accountability Module Stub
Provides comprehensive accountability frameworks and governance mechanisms for AI systems
Enables responsibility assignment, oversight mechanisms, and liability frameworks
:End Note

Type AccountabilityFramework is Dictionary with:
    framework_id as String
    framework_type as String
    responsibility_matrix as ResponsibilityMatrix
    oversight_mechanisms as List[OversightMechanism]
    audit_systems as List[AuditSystem]
    liability_framework as LiabilityFramework
    compliance_monitoring as ComplianceMonitoring
    remediation_procedures as List[RemediationProcedure]
    framework_configuration as FrameworkConfiguration

Type ResponsibilityMatrix is Dictionary with:
    matrix_id as String
    responsibility_assignments as List[ResponsibilityAssignment]
    authority_delegations as List[AuthorityDelegation]
    accountability_chains as List[AccountabilityChain]
    escalation_procedures as List[EscalationProcedure]
    matrix_validation as MatrixValidation

Type OversightMechanism is Dictionary with:
    mechanism_id as String
    mechanism_type as String
    oversight_scope as String
    oversight_procedures as List[OversightProcedure]
    oversight_authorities as List[OversightAuthority]
    oversight_frequency as String
    oversight_reporting as OversightReporting
    mechanism_effectiveness as Float

Type AuditSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    audit_type as String
    audit_scope as String
    audit_procedures as List[AuditProcedure]
    audit_criteria as List[AuditCriterion]
    audit_frequency as String
    audit_reporting as AuditReporting
    audit_compliance as AuditCompliance

Type LiabilityFramework is Dictionary with:
    framework_id as String
    liability_assignments as List[LiabilityAssignment]
    liability_limits as List[LiabilityLimit]
    liability_insurance as LiabilityInsurance
    liability_dispute_resolution as DisputeResolution
    liability_enforcement as LiabilityEnforcement

Type ComplianceMonitoring is Dictionary with:
    monitoring_id as String
    compliance_criteria as List[ComplianceCriterion]
    monitoring_frequency as String
    monitoring_procedures as List[MonitoringProcedure]
    compliance_reporting as ComplianceReporting
    violation_handling as ViolationHandling

Type RemediationProcedure is Dictionary with:
    procedure_id as String
    procedure_type as String
    remediation_steps as List[RemediationStep]
    remediation_timeline as String
    remediation_resources as List[RemediationResource]
    remediation_validation as RemediationValidation

Type ImplementationContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    implementation_requirements as Dictionary
    organizational_structure as Dictionary
    implementation_constraints as Dictionary
    context_metadata as Dictionary

Type OversightContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    oversight_requirements as Dictionary
    oversight_authorities as Dictionary
    oversight_constraints as Dictionary
    oversight_metadata as Dictionary

Type AuditContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    audit_requirements as Dictionary
    audit_scope as Dictionary
    audit_constraints as Dictionary
    audit_metadata as Dictionary

Type LiabilityContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    liability_requirements as Dictionary
    liability_constraints as Dictionary
    liability_metadata as Dictionary

Type ComplianceContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    compliance_requirements as Dictionary
    compliance_criteria as Dictionary
    compliance_metadata as Dictionary

Type IncidentContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    incident_description as String
    incident_severity as Float
    affected_parties as List[String]
    incident_metadata as Dictionary

Type MonitoringContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    monitoring_requirements as Dictionary
    effectiveness_criteria as Dictionary
    monitoring_metadata as Dictionary

Process called "create_accountability_framework" that takes config as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "implement_comprehensive_accountability" that takes accountability_framework as Dictionary and implementation_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "assign_responsibilities_and_authorities" that takes accountability_framework as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "implement_oversight_mechanisms" that takes accountability_framework as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "deploy_audit_systems" that takes accountability_framework as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "establish_liability_framework" that takes accountability_framework as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "configure_compliance_monitoring" that takes accountability_framework as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "conduct_accountability_audit" that takes accountability_framework as Dictionary and audit_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_remediation_procedures" that takes accountability_framework as Dictionary and incident_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "monitor_accountability_effectiveness" that takes accountability_framework as Dictionary and monitoring_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_accountability_monitoring_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_accountability_analysis" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary 